trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectNotFoundException" /> class exception is thrown when a requested object is not found in the underlying directory store.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectNotFoundException" /> 클래스 예외는 요청된 개체가 내부 디렉터리 저장소에 없으면 throw됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectNotFoundException" /> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectNotFoundException" /> class.
A message that describes the error.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectNotFoundException" /> class with a specified error message.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 오류 메시지를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectNotFoundException" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> object for the exception.
The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" /> for the exception.

Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectNotFoundException" /> class, using the specified serialization information and streaming context.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 serialization 정보와 스트리밍 컨텍스트를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectNotFoundException" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: A message that describes the error.
An <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> object that contains underlying exception information.
trans-unit.target: 내부 예외 정보가 포함된 <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectNotFoundException" /> class with a specified error message and an underlying exception object.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 오류 메시지와 내부 예외 개체를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectNotFoundException" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: A message that describes the error.
A <see cref="T:System.Type" /> object that describes the type of the requested object.
trans-unit.target: 요청된 개체의 형식을 설명하는 <see cref="T:System.Type" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the name of the requested object.

Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectNotFoundException" /> class with a specified error message and information about the requested object.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 오류 메시지와 요청된 개체에 대한 정보를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectNotFoundException" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> object that holds serialized object data about the exception that is being thrown.
trans-unit.target: throw되는 예외에 대한 serialize된 개체 데이터를 보유하는 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" /> object that contains contextual information about the source or destination.
trans-unit.target: 소스 또는 대상에 대한 컨텍스트 정보를 포함하는 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> object with information about the exception.
trans-unit.target: 예외에 대한 정보를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> 개체를 설정합니다.
